Title: Do not draw lines beyond canvas of graphs, do correct clipping
Level: 1
Edition: cee
Component: reporting
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1461596911

When in PDF documents you have graphs with lines that do not fit into the
selected vertical range then lines would be painted all over the paper -
way beyond the graph. This has now been fixed by introducing a correct clipping.
